Package: biomes
Title: Spatial Explicit Biome Maps and Assigning Species to Biomes
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Authors@R: 
    person("Alexander", "Zizka", , "alexander.zizka@biologie.uni-marburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1680-9192"))
Description: Contains rasterized global biome maps as provided by Fischer, Walentowitz & Beierkuhnlein (2022). TKTK biome schemes are available as terra raster objects, and two convenience functions help to assign geographic records and speceis to biomes. 
URL: https://github.com/azizka/biomer
